{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016eRmskrCh4df9rX7eexXMv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, WPM1 and greedy SAT didn't improve on the existing solutions. The comp02 greedy SAT didn't help either. Let me check if the soft clauses are unit for timetabling instances and look at what approaches might work better.\n\nFor comp02, greedy SAT ran but didn't improve. The softs aren't unit so core-guided won't work. Maybe we need a different approach.\n\nLet me think about what else to try:\n\n1. For timetabling non-unit: tabu search with existing solution, CWLS\n2. For heart/quantum-circuit: probably at local optima already\n\n\n3. The real opportunities are in correlation-clustering, haplotyping, and polysite-bloat where I should focus my efforts.\n\nI should also check whether the non-unit-soft instances might respond better to WPM1 with proper clause handling or if tabu search from the current best solutions would be more effective, then monitor the other running jobs and build targeted improvement scripts for the instances that haven't shown progress yet.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":246,"cache_creation_input_tokens":317,"cache_read_input_tokens":75399,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":317,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"38135602-62e8-4094-9f41-0f1fb730f536","uuid":"a502d1c6-8e33-4b17-a577-41502987a93d"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016eRmskrCh4df9rX7eexXMv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011vsEJkqEydFQ48dgmZgmzT","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /tmp/agent-sat-1\n# Write a script that uses tabu search from existing solution for timetabling\ncat > /tmp/solve_tabu_from_best.py << 'PYEOF'\n\"\"\"Tabu search from existing best solution for instances with medium nsofts\"\"\"\nimport sys, time, signal\nsys.path.insert(0, '/tmp/agent-sat-1')\nsignal.alarm(280)\n\nfrom library.wcnf_parser import parse_wcnf\nfrom library.solvers import build_occurrence_lists, tabu_search, walksat_soft, assignment_to_lits\nfrom library.clause_weight_ls import clause_weight_local_search\nfrom library.solutions import update_solution, load_solutions\n\nbase = \"benchmarks/max-sat-2024/mse24-anytime-weighted/\"\ninstances = {\n    0: \"timetabling_wt-comp02.wcnf\",\n    1: \"timetabling_wt-comp21.wcnf\",\n    2: \"timetabling_wt-comp09.wcnf\",\n    3: \"timetabling_wt-comp06.wcnf\",\n    4: \"timetabling_wt-test4.wcnf\",\n    5: \"MaxSATQueriesinInterpretableClassifiers_wt-heart_train_1_CNF_3_5.wcnf\",\n    6: \"quantum-circuit-grover-noancilla_4_52_ibmq-casablanca_7.wcnf\",\n    7: \"causal-discovery_wt-causal_Water_10_100.wcnf\",\n    8: \"causal-discovery_wt-causal_Bands_6_277.wcnf\",\n    9: \"abstraction-refinement_wt-downcast-pmd.wcnf\",\n    10: \"setcover_wt-rail507.wcnf\",\n    11: \"setcover_wt-rail582.wcnf\",\n}\n\nidx = int(sys.argv[1])\ninst = instances[idx]\nprint(f\"Working on {inst}\")\nt0 = time.time()\n\ndata = parse_wcnf(base + inst)\nnvars = data['nvars']\nhards = data['hard_clauses']\nsofts = data['soft_clauses']\nprint(f\"nvars={nvars}, nhards={len(hards)}, nsofts={len(softs)}\")\n\nsolutions = load_solutions()\nif inst not in solutions:\n    print(\"No existing solution!\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\ncurrent_best = solutions[inst]['cost']\nconfig = solutions[inst]['configuration']\nprint(f\"Starting from cost={current_best}\")\n\nassignment = bytearray(nvars + 1)\nfor lit in config:\n    v = abs(lit)\n    if v <= nvars:\n        assignment[v] = 1 if lit > 0 else 0\n\nocc = build_occurrence_lists(nvars, hards, softs)\n\n# CWLS is generally the strongest local search\nremaining = 260 - (time.time() - t0)\nif remaining > 30:\n    rt = remaining - 10\n    print(f\"CWLS ({rt:.0f}s)...\")\n    best_assign, best_cost = clause_weight_local_search(\n        assignment, softs, hards, occ, timeout=rt, smooth_probability=0.003\n    )\n    if best_cost < current_best:\n        lits = assignment_to_lits(best_assign)\n        if update_solution(inst, best_cost, lits, \"cwls-deep\"):\n            current_best = best_cost\n            print(f\"  -> {best_cost}\")\n\nprint(f\"Done: best={current_best} in {time.time()-t0:.1f}s\")\nwith open('/tmp/agent-sat-1/experiments.log', 'a') as f:\n    f.write(f\"[{time.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}] instance: {inst} | approach: cwls-deep | cost: {current_best} | time: {time.time()-t0:.1f} | notes: tabu-from-best\\n\")\nPYEOF\necho \"Ready\"","description":"Write tabu-from-best solver script"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":246,"cache_creation_input_tokens":317,"cache_read_input_tokens":75399,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":317,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"38135602-62e8-4094-9f41-0f1fb730f536","uuid":"87f04b45-46e8-41bc-9c3c-12ba6b2653c1"}
